element.name: Milverton by Windsockers, Traditional Cache (1/1)

description.center: An old Cemetery of the minute town of "Milverton"

long-description.p:
Most of the locals (except those that live right next to it) don't even know about this cemetery, which neverthelesss still appears in use. Some of the graves are really old, although it is hard to tell how old exactly as their prints have become unreadable. This cemetery is in a nice location, and the cache can easily be combined with
Eaglais agus Túr and
Ardgillan Castle.
If you want to visit this cache by public transport, follow the instructions for Ardgillan Castle.

element.encoded-hints: You'll have to find this one on your own.
